---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
const days = await getCollection('days');
const totalDays = days.length;
---
<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_220px] gap-8 md:gap-10 items-end">
    <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
      <header class="eyebrow-pair">
        <span class="ey-left">第 {totalDays} 篇</span>
        <span class="ey-right">一份持續書寫的工作日誌</span>
      </header>
      <h1 class="font-display text-ink leading-[0.98] tracking-[-0.02em] text-balance"
          style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5.5vw, 4.5rem);">
        我幫台灣團隊<br />把 AI 工具<em class="italic text-teal">落地。</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="lede mt-5 max-w-xl">
        9 年新創軟體開發經驗（iOS → DevRel → Full Stack）、前 iOS@Taipei 社群主持人。過去 {totalDays} 天每天公開實作 AI 工作流——現在幫你的團隊把這套方法搬進生產環境。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-baseline">
        <a href="#inquire" class="btn-ink">聊聊合作 →</a>
        <a href="/days" class="btn-ghost">看看作品</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="order-1 md:order-2 max-w-[260px] md:max-w-none">
      <figure>
        <div class="relative">
          <span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-full h-full bg-ochre"></span>
          <img
            src="/dawson.webp"
            alt="Dawson Wang"
            width="640"
            height="800"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            decoding="async"
            class="relative block w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover grayscale-[15%] border border-ink"
          />
        </div>
        <figcaption class="mt-3 font-sans text-[10px] tracking-[.22em] uppercase text-muted font-semibold flex justify-between items-baseline">
          <span>Dawson Wang</span>
          <span class="text-brick">已寫 {totalDays} 篇</span>
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
